author: Elizabeth and Martin
title: Elizabeth and Martin
text: Having Frank manage our properties has been fantastic. His knowledge and expertise in property management means that we can sit back and trust his judgement not only in tenant selection but in every aspect of managing our properties. He conducts scheduled property inspections thoroughly to ensure that our properties are properly maintained by our tenants. We are now stress free and happy investors.
